{
  "stem": "166.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we marched out to five, we had to hold each other with locked in the hand to five, and march all the time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was, with a gun, a guard on this side and a guard on this side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were going-- every 50 feet, there was a guard like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we marched-- 5,000 people-- we marched from Blechhammer to work every morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then at the end of the day, we waited at the gate, and marched into camp-- back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The march was maybe a half hour from camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when the guards came in-- when we marched into the factory that was the [GERMAN], they called it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was so big that they were connected together with the IG Farben from the other side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The guards came and they went apart, through the whole factory, and they guarded the whole factory-- the whole plant, they guarded.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When we marched in the, the [NON-ENGLISH], they marched into the factory and the guards went all the way around, and we were inside free.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But in that camp-- in that plant, there were working Russian prisoners of war, French prisoners of war, English prisoners of war, so many Poles with the the P on what they were forced to come-- and then they had [NON-ENGLISH] on it, Russians.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I worked there for-- they put me in a kommando, also, low voltage for Siemens-Halske.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I worked on telephones.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they take us--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we were standing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Appell, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We locked arms.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We marched, we marched into the plant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Into the plant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the guards went to the outside of the plant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We marched inside the plant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And each kommando had a different trade.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
